720435f-a.title: Manhattan: Amsterdam Avenue - 173rd Street
720435f-a.text:
Highbridge Park: the kntrance to the Highbridge Play Center
on Amsterdam Avenue anc 173rd Street. View 2 is south from the
Park, showing Manhattan skyscrapers in the distance.
P. L. Sperr  June 20, 1940
NO PTPPODUCTIONS  Views 11,2
